query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `feedbacks` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `type` enum('CORRETIVO','POSITIVO') NOT NULL,
  `title` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `content` text NOT NULL,
  `imageUrl` varchar(500),
  `rating` int,
  `sessionType` enum('ORDINARIA','EXTRAORDINARIA','COMISSAO','PLENARIO') NOT NULL,
  `sessionNum` varchar(50),
  `categories` json,
  `isRead` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `readAt` timestamp,
  `revisorId` int NOT NULL,
  `taquigId` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `feedbacks_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  KEY `feedbacks_revisor_idx` (`revisorId`),
  KEY `feedbacks_taquig_idx` (`taquigId`),
  KEY `feedbacks_type_idx` (`type`),
  KEY `feedbacks_isRead_idx` (`isRead`),
  KEY `feedbacks_createdAt_idx` (`createdAt`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `comments` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `content` text NOT NULL,
  `feedbackId` int NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `comments_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  KEY `comments_feedback_idx` (`feedbackId`),
  KEY `comments_user_idx` (`userId`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `reactions` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `type` enum('ENTENDI','OBRIGADO','VOU_MELHORAR') NOT NULL,
  `feedbackId` int NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `reactions_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  KEY `reactions_feedback_idx` (`feedbackId`),
  KEY `reactions_user_idx` (`userId`),
  KEY `reactions_type_idx` (`type`),
  UNIQUE KEY `reactions_feedback_user_type` (`feedbackId`, `userId`, `type`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `avisos` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `type` enum('COTIDIANO','URGENTE','RECORRENTE') NOT NULL,
  `title` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `content` text NOT NULL,
  `targets` json,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `avisos_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  KEY `avisos_type_idx` (`type`),
  KEY `avisos_createdAt_idx` (`createdAt`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `aviso_reads` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `avisoId` int NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `readAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `aviso_reads_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  KEY `aviso_reads_aviso_idx` (`avisoId`),
  KEY `aviso_reads_user_idx` (`userId`),
  UNIQUE KEY `aviso_reads_aviso_user` (`avisoId`, `userId`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `templates` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `content` text NOT NULL,
  `category` varchar(100),
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `templates_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
